# Default `npm start` discovers your Mac from Expo (same Wi‑Fi as the phone).
# Override only if needed (wrong host or USB-only with adb reverse):
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://192.168.1.10:5051
# EXPO_PUBLIC_SCAN_API_URL=http://192.168.1.10:8000
#
# USB + Expo on 127.0.0.1: use `npm run start:localhost` and keep Backend + Scan on the Mac.
